metadata.name: The two sides of the same coin
metadata.description:
In societies around the world, mine included, women are still to this day defined with two terms ''respectable'' and ''dishonorable'' , they are always divided and the reasons differ. 

This picture for me is a way to fight back, a way to show that these brackets were put on are meaningless, and women are created with the two halves together, two sides of the same coin.
